        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin:0;"><strong>Result delivered:</strong> 20 drafted emails sitting in your CRM, ready for a rep to review and send.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="service-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">manage_search</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.0625rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Research &amp; Analysis</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.625rem;"><strong>Task received:</strong> "Summarize what our top 5 competitors changed about their pricing this quarter."</p>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.625rem;"><strong>Agent acts:</strong> Searches public sources, reads pricing pages and press coverage, cross-checks dates, and structures the findings by competitor.</p>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin:0;"><strong>Result delivered:</strong> A one-page structured report with sources cited, delivered in minutes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="service-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">support_agent</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.0625rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Customer Service</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.625rem;"><strong>Task received:</strong> A customer emails asking where their order is and whether it can still be changed.</p>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.625rem;"><strong>Agent acts:</strong> Looks up the order status, checks whether it has shipped, and replies with the answer, or a change confirmation if it's still possible.</p>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin:0;"><strong>Result delivered:</strong> Customer gets an answer in seconds, any time of day.</p>
      </div>
