        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Agents monitor shipment status across carriers, proactively contact customers when delays occur, update internal systems, and escalate exceptions to your ops team only when human intervention is genuinely needed.</p>
      </div>
